                            <comment id="17726490" author="bereng" created="Fri, 26 May 2023 05:57:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=adelapena&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;adelapena&quot;&gt;adelapena&lt;/a&gt; this should be a quick one as we&apos;ve already talked about it. If you&apos;re happy I&apos;ll push the rest of the PRs.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17726603" author="adelapena" created="Fri, 26 May 2023 12:12:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Looks good to me, I have left a couple of nits on the PR. This should also be applied to 3.0 and 3.11, since the automatic detection also exists on those branches. By the way, shouldn&apos;t this be a new feature rather than a bug?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17726610" author="adelapena" created="Fri, 26 May 2023 12:29:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=bereng&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;bereng&quot;&gt;bereng&lt;/a&gt; you might be interested in being second reviewer on &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-17997&quot; title=&quot;Improve git branch handling for CircleCI generate.sh&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-17997&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-17997&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. It adds a parameter to specify the base branch, which is one of the reasons why the detector of changes sometimes adds more tests than expected when the patch hasn&apos;t been rebased in a while.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17729659" author="bereng" created="Tue, 6 Jun 2023 08:37:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-17997&quot; title=&quot;Improve git branch handling for CircleCI generate.sh&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-17997&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-17997&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; should merge soon. Let&apos;s wait and I&apos;ll get this done.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17730050" author="adelapena" created="Wed, 7 Jun 2023 10:17:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve just merged &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-17997&quot; title=&quot;Improve git branch handling for CircleCI generate.sh&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-17997&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-17997&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17730092" author="bereng" created="Wed, 7 Jun 2023 12:11:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I was going to, just waiting on your +1 so thanks. I&apos;ll do this next &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/smile.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
